OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright spells possible at
OL,6,Ffirst. Otherwise becoming cloudy and
OL,7,Fwindy with rain spreading east through
OL,8,Fthe morning, heavy and persistent at
OL,9,Ftimes. Clear spells and blustery
OL,10,Fshowers spreading in from the west
OL,11,Fthrough the afternoon. Strong winds at
OL,12,Ftimes.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FClear spells and scattered
OL,15,Fshowers through the evening and
OL,16,Fovernight, these showers heavy and
OL,17,Fblustery at times. Occasionally strong
OL,18,Fsouthwest winds, veering westerly
OL,19,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
