OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,6,Fshowers in the morning, showers
OL,7,Fbecoming less frequent in the
OL,8,Fafternoon allowing longer sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Strong winds at first easing
OL,10,Fby day. Cooler than recent days.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCold
OL,13,Fstart on Saturday then bright spells
OL,14,Fand a few showers, these mainly in the
OL,15,Fwest. Cloudy and windier on Sunday and
OL,16,FMonday with further rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
